title: dryadforestinteract
body:
The rain feels so good on my leaves...
What do you want?
[[Can you help me?|foresthelp]][[Let's chat|forestchat]][[Where am I?|forestinfo]][[Let's talk later|forestleave]]

title: forestinfo
body:
This is the Fiendish Forest...
I don't think it's *that* dangerous...
Mostly the trees here annoy me!
They all think they are SO special just cause they live in one place...
*huff*
[[It's pretty scary here...|infoend]][[The trees don't look so bad...|infoend]]

title: forestleave
body:
Until next time...
If you ever back to the school...
[[An optimist as always...|forestleaveend]][[If I even want to make it back...|forestleaveend]]

title: ENTspeech
body:
What are you doing in my forest?!
[[I didn't come here by choice...|ENT1]][[What makes it your forest?|ENT2]]

title: ENT1
body:
So?!
GET OUT!
I can tell you're a woman and women DO AS THEY ARE TOLD!

title: ENT2
body:
I am the oldest male tree in this forest!
That makes it mine!

title: ENTcling
body:
Wait...
Come back!
[[What in the world do you want?|entcling1]][[Okay fine...|entcling2]]

title: dryadhelp1
body:
Watch out for that ENT over there...
Can you say stage 5 clinger?
<<dryadhelpend>>
